false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA time will come to people when a man will go around with gold to give in charity, but he will find no one to accept it, and a single man will be seen followed by forty women\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14644,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/08\/your-hour-starts-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":17324,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Death: Your personal Hour starts when you die","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Some men among the rough bedouins came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and they said, \u201cWhen is the Hour?\u201d The Prophet looked to the youngest of them and he said, \u201cIf this boy lives, he will not reach old age before your Hour is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43264,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/19\/hadith-on-euphrates-trial-over-treasure-before-the-hour\/","url_meta":{"origin":17324,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Euphrates: Trial over treasure before the Hour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 19, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSoon the Euphrates River will disclose a treasure of gold. Whoever witnesses it, let him not take anything